      <div id="property">يوللانغان ۋاقتى :  2010-02-24 19:58:13&nbsp;&nbsp;يوللغۇچى :  <a href="/member/member.php?username=yarkn&channelid=43" class="member_url">yarkn</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;كۆرۈلۈش سانى : <span id="hits">631</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="myitem.php?action=add" target="_blank"><font color="#FF0000">مەنمۇ ئەسەر يوللايمەن </font></a></div>
